# starlette CVEs requiring starlette ≥1.0 — FastAPI 0.x depends on starlette 0.4x.
# FastAPI has not yet released a 1.0 that uses starlette 1.x.
# These CVEs relate to SSRF via UNC paths (Windows-only, not applicable to our Linux
# containers) and DoS via form limits (mitigated by nginx rate limiting upstream).
# Review date: 2026-07-09
CVE-2026-48818
CVE-2026-54283
CVE-2025-62727

# pyasn1 CVE — python-jose pins pyasn1<0.5.0, cannot upgrade independently.
# DoS via unbounded recursion — mitigated by request size limits at nginx.
# Review date: 2026-07-09
CVE-2026-30922
